Package: ansistyle
Title: Style Console Output with Ansi Escape Sequences
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(
    "Brodie", "Gaslam", email="brodie.gaslam@yahoo.com",
    role=c("aut", "cre")),
    person(
    "Gabor", "Csardi", email="csardi.gabor@gmail.com",
    role=c("cph"),
    comment="Copied parts of sources of crayon package"))
Description: Stripped down dependency-less version of the `crayon` package by
    Gabor Csardi. Modifies character vectors by adding ANSI escape sequences to
    render text with style in terminals that support ANSI style escape sequences.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.2)
Suggests:
    testthat,
    covr
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
